## 3. `.gitignore`

Create `.gitignore` at the root:

```gitignore
# Byte-compiled / optimized / DLL files
__pycache__/
*.py[cod]
*$py.class

# C extensions
*.so

# Virtual environments
.env
.venv
env/
venv/
ENV/

# VS Code
.vscode/
.history/

# Jupyter
.ipynb_checkpoints/

# macOS
.DS_Store

# Python packaging
build/
dist/
*.egg-info/

# Plots and outputs
*.png
*.pdf
*.svg
*.eps

# Logs
*.log
